Recommends: gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, gstreamer1.0-gtk4, gstreamer1.0-tools
Description: GTK nutrient tracker for narrow Linux phone screens
 Nutrients tracks daily calories, protein, carbohydrates, and fat in a
 phone-sized GTK 4 and Libadwaita interface.
 .
 It supports editable goals, a monthly overview, Open Food Facts searches,
 and optional camera-based barcode scanning.
